|-root
  |-components
    |-Navbar.js
    |-Footer.js
  |-styles
    |-global.css 
    |-navbar.module.css   
    |-footer.module.css        
  |-pages
    |-api
      |-users.js
    |-index.js
  |-utils
    |- dbConnect.js


Lets say we want to import dbConnect.js from pages/api/user.js

Relative import:
import dbConnect from '../../utils/dbConnect';

Absolute import:
import dbConnect from 'src/utils/dbConnect';
